msgstr "When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.212, sc5
msgctxt "sn3.21:5.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, puriso pathaviyā vā pallaṅkaṃ āroheyya, pallaṅkā vā assapiṭṭhiṃ āroheyya, assapiṭṭhiyā vā hatthikkhandhaṃ āroheyya, hatthikkhandhā vā pāsādaṃ āroheyya. "
msgstr "This person is like someone who ascends from the ground to a couch; from a couch to horseback; from horseback to an elephant; and from an elephant to a stilt longhouse. "

msgctxt "sn3.21:5.2"
msgid "Tathūpamāhaṃ, mahārāja, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn3.21:5.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, mahārāja, puggalo tamojotiparāyano hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is dark and bound for light. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.95, sc6
msgctxt "sn3.21:6.1"
msgid "Kathañca, mahārāja, puggalo jotitamaparāyano hoti? "
msgstr "And how is a person light and bound for darkness? "

msgctxt "sn3.21:6.2"
msgid "Idha, mahārāja, ekacco puggalo ucce kule paccājāto hoti, khattiyamahāsālakule vā brāhmaṇamahāsālakule vā gahapatimahāsālakule vā, aḍḍhe mahaddhane mahābhoge pahūtajātarūparajate pahūtavittūpakaraṇe pahūtadhanadhaññe. "
msgstr "It’s when some person is reborn in an eminent family—a well-to-do family of aristocrats, brahmins, or householders—rich, affluent, and wealthy, with lots of gold and silver, lots of property and assets, and lots of money and grain. "

msgctxt "sn3.21:6.3"
msgid "So ca hoti abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko, paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgato, lābhī annassa pānassa vatthassa yānassa mālāgandhavilepanassa seyyāvasathapadīpeyyassa. "
msgstr "And they’re attractive, good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty. They get to have food, drink, clothes, and vehicles; garlands, perfumes, and makeup; and bed, house, and lighting. "

msgctxt "sn3.21:6.4"
